        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post TIM CELLA - LENGTH x WIDTH Mobile: (631) 553-8984 LUXURY APARTMENTS (EAST VILLAGE / GRAMERCY) $5700 - LARGE JUNIOR 2-BEDROOM (BRAND NEW KITCHEN + CLOSETS GALORE!) Recently renovated, the oversized apartment homes feature high ceilings, hardwood floors, large windows, expansive living rooms with separate dining areas, spacious bedrooms that easily accommodate king size beds, custom bathrooms, ample closet space, and windowed kitchens with modern appliances -- all with the choice between two finishes: Modern and Classic. The residences are pet-friendly, and all utilities are included. The recently-renovated apartment homes offer expansive living spaces. Central to Stuyvesant Town is the iconic \"Oval\" with its large open lawn, water fountain, and amenity spaces. A large array of amenities provide endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle and interests: a state of the art fitness facility, full-service concierge, social events, seasonal greenmarket & ice skating rink, recreational courts and playgrounds, tournaments, and the list goes on! Apartment Features: Air Conditioning High Speed Internet Access Dishwasher Microwave Walk-In Closets Fitness & Recreation: Basketball Court Premier Fitness Center Seasonal Ice-Skating Rink Playground Unique Features: 24/7 Public Safety 80- acre Park Setting Cafe Community Center Dog-Walking/Pet Care Full-Service Concierge On-site Movers Private Shuttle to Midtown Seasonal Greenmarket Courtesy Patrol Day Care House Sitter Services Laundry Facilities Maid Service Maintenance on site Package Service Property Manager on Site NO BROKER FEE (EXACT FLOORPLAN!) TIM CELLA LENGTH x WIDTH LICENSED REAL ESTATE SALESPERSON Mobile: (631) 553-8984 I specialize in: Gramercy, Murray Hill, Midtown East, Sutton Place and The Upper East Side. We at Length x Width work hard to find you the perfect property. Whether you are looking for a no fee apartment in Midtown West or a loft in SoHo, we have access to thousands of listings and can help. We have agents who specialize in: Brooklyn (Park Slope, Williamsburg, Bushwick, Fort Greene, Cobble Hill, and more!), Queens (Astoria, Long Island City, Rego Park, Forest Hills, Flushing, Ridgewood and more!), Staten Island and The Bronx (Riverdale, Pelham, Marble Hill and more!).. In Manhattan our Agents specialize in Battery Park, the Financial District, Tribeca, SoHo, Nolita, the Lower East Side, the East Village, the West Village, Greenwich Village, Chelsea, Union Square, the Flatiron District, Gramercy Park, Murray Hill, Midtown East, Midtown West, the Upper East Side, the Upper West Side, Harlem, Washington Heights and Inwood. We have agents who specialize in Pet Friendly Buildings, Roommates, International Clients, Penthouses and more! So if you're looking for pet friendly sublet or a large prewar apartment on Park Avenue, contact Length x Width today! Thinking about purchasing an apartment or investment property? Length x Width can help with that also.",
