        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Massive Ridgewood 3BR/2BA w/ Balcony + W/D in Unit! 🧺🥹 Come check out this spacious 3-bedroom / 2-bathroom apartment occupying the entire 2nd floor of a townhouse! Featuring two separate common areas, a private balcony, and excellent natural light throughout, this unique home offers plenty of space to spread out and relax! AMENITIES: → Washer / Dryer In Unit → Private Balcony → Video Intercom System HIGHLIGHTS: → Stainless Steel Appliances → Hardwood Flooring → Central Air & Heat → Entire Second Floor Apartment → Separate Living Room → Separate Dining Room → Separate Kitchen w/ Windows → Two Distinct Common Areas → Spacious Bedrooms → Great Natural Light → Large Windows → Ample Closet Space → 2 Full Bathrooms (Tub + Showers) RENTAL DETAILS: → Available ASAP → Heat / Hot Water Included → Pets Upon Approval → Guarantors Accepted → First + Security TRANSIT: → (L) at Jefferson St = 0.7 miles → (L) at Halsey St = 0.8 miles Text or email me today to arrange a tour! Myles - (914) 873-4913 , or you can email me directly through this ad . I have a video tour of this space available upon request! PHOTOS OF ACTUAL UNIT 😊 Not the one for you? Check out our website to find more apartments, some of which are NOT on StreetEasy 🤫 😊 https://rennit.nyc/apartments Myles Ellison Lic. Assoc. R.E. Broker @ Rennit Lic. # 10301221434",
