        "geocode_query": "",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to apartment 5 of 42 Avenue B, a boutique building located in prime East Village. Available for July 7th occupancy, this thoughtfully renovated one bedroom apartment offers modern living including an updated kitchen(with dishwasher), a spacious living room, queen sized bedroom, modern bathroom, an in-unit Bosch washer and dryer, and a balcony. The bedroom has a closet and there is an additional hall closet. This apartment is complimented by exposed brick, high ceilings, and hardwood floors throughout. Ideally located between East 3rd and East 4th Street, you will be ten minutes from St Marks Place, 5 minutes to Tompkins Square Park and steps to many of the neighborhood’s best restaurants and stores. This location offers easy transit access as you will be a short walk to the F and J train and 3 blocks to the crosstown bus. The building has a virtual doorman and is pet friendly. This is a walk up building, the apartment is on the second floor. Fees to rent this apartment are 1st months rent, 1 month security deposit, 20 dollar application fee. Tenants must make 40x the monthly rent (179,000) and have good credit(680 and above). Heat and hot water are included, tenant is responsible for electricity and internet. Guarantors(third party and personal) are welcomed. Please call for showings or if you have questions. video- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rfj7STDxaRI Sarah Rosenfeld (Real Estate Salesperson) (R New York) (646-335-8383)",
