        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post LOOKING FOR A 2 BEDROOM FOR $2400-2500? YOU CAN HIRE A BROKER... We are showing 2BRs at a lower option of 2400 when hired as tenant's Broker vs. the \"no-fee\" option of $2700. PLEASE READ THE WHOLE LISTING + SEND YOUR INFO 👇 WE WILL NOT SHOW YOU AN APT WITHOUT YOUR RECEIVING YOUR INFO Working with a Licensed Broker is legal and often the smarter choice. Many \"no‑fee\" listings simply build the fee into the rent, costing you more money over time. “No fee = higher rent” or “lower rent = with a fee,” and the lower‑rent option is usually cheaper overall. For example, $2400 (with a 1‑month broker fee) vs. $2700 (no fee) is a $3600 yearly difference. Rent increases are based on the lower‑rent amount. Please let us know in your email that you read this part and are aware of the broker fee. Great 2BR apt in a walk-up building (4th floor), perfect for a roommates/couple. Separate kitchen, ideal for cooking and dining at home. Spacious living room, 2 real bedrooms, great closets, full bathroom. 4fl Walk UP. Laundry in building. Steps from shops, restaurants, and cafes. Excellent transit access. Move-in ready by August 1. Please send your information: No information, no response. Please don't waste our time Single/Couple— how many occupants Annual Income + Credit Score Earliest Move-in Date Pet info (type + size) Your Number: Guarantor info (if you need one) : Areas= This ad is for a 2BR in Kensington is $2400 with a 1 Month Broker fee 40x times the rent; Guarantor 80x BY CONTACTING US, YOUR AGREE TO WORK WORK WITH A LICENSED RE BROKER AND ACKNOWLEDGE THAT A BROKR'S FEE WILL APPLY ONLY IF YOU RENT ONE OF OUR UNITS. PLEASE... NO EMAILS ASKING \"IS THE APT AVAILABLE.\" WE WONT ANSWER. PLEASE SEND YOUR INFORMATION OR WE WON'T ANSWER GREAT APT, LOOKING FOR GREAT PEOPLE! KENSINGTON| PROSPECT PARK SLOPE SOUTH GREENWOOD BROOKLYN",
