        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Private Balcony, bedroom with corner windows on both sides, in unit washer dryer, dishwasher, full living room with windows! - Discover contemporary luxury in the heart of Flatbush! - Designed by the renowned Amr Ouda of Jay Architect & Engineering, 2404 Cortelyou Rd is a stunning new 7 story/26 unit corner luxury elevator building, offering a mix of sunny, spacious and super large 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments designed for effortless modern living. Brand new luxury elevator building with gym/fitness room, bike room, access to shared outdoor spaces such as a deck on the 2nd and the 6th floor as well as the building's rooftop. - Inquire to learn more about the option to rent a car parking spot for a separate monthly charge Great location near the B, Q, 2, and 5 train lines, minutes away from grocery stores, bars, restaurants, cafes, and all your shopping needs. Located on Cortelyou Rd corner Flatbush Ave in Brooklyn’s beautiful Flatbush, an up and coming neighborhood in the heart of New York City’s most charming borough, boasting tree lined streets, stunning architecture, enchanting parks, and a diverse yet welcoming atmosphere, all within close proximity to the city’s bustling urban hubs. This luxury Brooklyn apartment building offers large 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments in Flatbush that feature unobstructed views, super spacious layouts, and in unit washer dryer! If you’re searching for a Flatbush apartment, this new development is ready to welcome you home. Apartment features include modern open-concept designs. Sleek finishes and modern hardware add a contemporary edge, while large, oversized windows flood the apartments with an abundance of natural light. Kitchens come equipped with premium stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher. Features also include an in-unit washer/dryer, spacious bathrooms, large closets, split units for air conditioning and heat, hardwood floors throughout, and a video intercom system!",
