        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Entire 2nd floor of a 2 story townhouse! 3 bedroom apartment with separate kitchen with windows, separate living room, separate dining room, in unit washer dryer & Private Balcony! - Located on 54th St and Arnold Ave right off Metropolitan Ave, great location, border Ridgewood and Bushwick (Brooklyn), 10-15 minute walk to the L train ar Jefferson St stop near Maria Hernandez Park, many bars, shops, and great night life area…or the Bus stops right outside and goes directly into Williamsburg. This is the entire 2nd floor, of a 3 unit, 2 story house, 3 spacious bedrooms, all with great windows and closets, in unit washer dryer, bathroom with tub and shower, windows in your kitchen, 2 completely separate common spaces, so you'll have 2 living rooms or you can use one for separate dining and one for separate living room, private balcony, in unit washer dryer, guarantors accepted, pets allowed * upon approval only",
