        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Private Backyard, in unit washer dryer duplex apartment, 1 bedroom + a finished basement space and 2 full baths! - Located on 54th St and Arnold Ave right off Metropolitan Ave, great location, border Ridgewood and Bushwick (Brooklyn), 10-15 minute walk to the L train ar Jefferson St stop near Maria Hernandez Park, many bars, shops, and great night life area…or the Bus stops right outside and goes directly into Williamsburg. - Note: Per NYC regulations, basements are not a legal sleeping/living space, it should be for recreational or storage use only, renter's insurance is strongly recommended, keep your personal items elevated and not directly on the ground due to risks of water, floods and sewer backups during heavy rain Large Private Backyard, in unit washer dryer, kitchen with windows allowing tons of natural light, spacious bedroom with windows and closets, large finished basement space, 2 full baths, one on each level, both with standing showers only, sorry no tub, in unit washer dryer, guarantors accepted, pets allowed * upon approval only",
