        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post August 1st lease start date only NO DISHWASHER Large, open and sunny studio apartment in Brand New Building! - Located on South 6th St and Berry St, Prime Williamsburg, 8 min walk to the Marcy Ave J M Z and a 13 min walk to the Bedford Ave L trains, or, for a refreshing commute, hop on the water taxi at Schaefer Landing. - Just steps to the new coveted Domino Park, with foodie-friendly cafes, craft beer bars, ice cream shops, and enough nightlife to carry you through into the morning. Before you head out the door, grab a coffee and homemade pastry at Butler & Co.! Apartment: Washer dryer in unit, Central air and heat, video intercom system, hardwood flooring, modern kitchen with high end stainless steal appliances including stove and microwave, modern bathroom, in unit washer dryer! - Good income and credit score required, guarantors accepted, pet friendly *upon approval only, no brokers fee, showings by appointment only.",
