        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post virtual tour- https://listings.piiqvr.com/viewer?token=q_pCVRLb Welcome to apartment 3B of 234 West 14th Street, a well maintained elevator building located in the heart of the West Village. Available for August 3rd occupancy, this renovated one bedroom apartment combined classic charm with modern updates in a highly desirable location. This residence features an upgraded kitchen with stainless steel appliances(plus a dishwasher and wine cooler), a sunny living room with exposed brick and high ceilings, a marble bathroom, and an in-unit Bosch washer and dryer. The bedroom fits a queen bed and has two large windows. This spacious apartment is complimented by a lot of natural light and crown moldings. The building has a virtual doorman, a package room, and a pet friendly policy. Ideally located between seventh and eight avenue you will be a ten minute walk to the Meatpacking district, 15 minutes to Union Square, and steps to many of the neighborhood's best restaurants and stores. You will also be a 5 minute walk to all train lines(F, M, A, C, E, 1, 2) and one block to the crosstown bus. Fees to rent this apartment are 1st month rent, 1 month security deposit, 20 dollar application fee. Heat and hot water are included, tenant is responsible for electricity and internet. Tenants must make 40x the monthly rent (219,000) and have good credit(680 and above). Guarantors(third party and personal) are welcome. Please call for showings or if you have questions. Sarah Rosenfeld (Real Estate Salesperson) (R New York) (646-335-8383)",
